msgstr "Strategi Harga Paket"

msgid ""
"How to calculate bundle price. Fixed: Use the price field. Percentage "
"Discount: Apply discount to component sum. Components Sum: Total of all "
"components."
msgstr ""
"Bagaimana cara menghitung harga paket. Tetap: Gunakan bidang harga. Diskon "
"Persentase: Terapkan diskon ke jumlah komponen. Jumlah Komponen: Total semua"
" komponen."

msgid "Bundle Discount Percentage"
msgstr "Persentase Diskon Paket"

#, python-format
msgid ""
"Discount percentage off component total (e.g., 15.00 for 15% off). Only used"
" with 'Percentage Discount' strategy."
msgstr ""
"Persentase diskon dari total komponen (misalnya, 15.00 untuk diskon 15%). "
"Hanya digunakan dengan strategi 'Diskon Persentase'."

msgid "Customer Chooses Amount"
msgstr "Pelanggan Memilih Jumlah"

