msgid "Connect License Provider - Setup Instructions"
msgstr "Hubungkan Pemegang Lisensi - Petunjuk Pengaturan"

msgid ""
"\n"
"                <h3>Spwig Built-in License Server</h3>\n"
"                <p>Spwig's built-in license management server is fully-managed and requires no external setup!</p>\n"
"                <ol>\n"
"                    <li>In the next step, you'll enter your Spwig Built-in License Server credentials</li>\n"
"                    <li>If you don't have an account yet, sign up at: <a href=\"https://licenses.spwig.com\" target=\"_blank\">licenses.spwig.com</a></li>\n"
"                    <li>After signing up, you'll receive your Account ID and API Key</li>\n"
"                </ol>\n"
"                <div class=\"alert alert-info\">\n"
"                    <strong>Recommended:</strong> The built-in license server provides the easiest integration with full feature support.\n"
"                </div>\n"
"            "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"                <h3>Spwig Server Lisensi Bawaan</h3> <p>Server manajemen lisensi bawaan Spwig sepenuhnya dikelola dan tidak memerlukan pengaturan eksternal!</p> <ol> <li>Pada langkah berikutnya, Anda akan memasukkan kredensial Server Lisensi Bawaan Spwig Anda</li> <li>Jika Anda belum memiliki akun, daftarkan diri Anda di: <a href=\"https://licenses.spwig.com\" target=\"_blank\">licenses.spwig.com</a></li> <li>Setelah mendaftar, Anda akan menerima ID Akun dan API Key Anda</li> </ol> <div class=\"alert alert-info\"> <strong>Dianjurkan:</strong> Server lisensi bawaan menyediakan integrasi yang paling mudah dengan dukungan fitur penuh. </div>\n"
"            "

msgid ""
"\n"
"                <h3>Keygen.sh Setup</h3>\n"
"                <ol>\n"
"                    <li>Sign up for a Keygen.sh account at <a href=\"https://keygen.sh\" target=\"_blank\">keygen.sh</a></li>\n"
"                    <li>Create a new product in your Keygen dashboard</li>\n"
"                    <li>Create a policy for your product (defines license terms)</li>\n"
"                    <li>Generate a Product API Token: Settings → Tokens → Create Product Token</li>\n"
"                    <li>Note your Account ID from the URL: app.keygen.sh/accounts/<strong>YOUR_ACCOUNT_ID</strong></li>\n"
"                </ol>\n"
"                <p>You'll need: <strong>Account ID</strong> and <strong>Product API Token</strong></p>\n"
"            "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"                <h3>Pengaturan Keygen.sh</h3> <ol> <li>Buat akun Keygen.sh di <a href=\"https://keygen.sh\" target=\"_blank\">keygen.sh</a></li> <li>Buat produk baru di dashboard Keygen Anda</li> <li>Buat kebijakan untuk produk Anda (menentukan syarat lisensi)</li> <li>Generasikan Token API Produk: Pengaturan → Token → Buat Token Produk</li> <li>Catat ID Akun Anda dari URL: app.keygen.sh/accounts/<strong>YOUR_ACCOUNT_ID</strong></li> </ol> <p>Anda memerlukan: <strong>ID Akun</strong> dan <strong>Token API Produk</strong></p>\n"
"            "

msgid ""
"\n"
"                <h3>License Spring Setup</h3>\n"
"                <ol>\n"
"                    <li>Sign up for License Spring at <a href=\"https://licensespring.com\" target=\"_blank\">licensespring.com</a></li>\n"
"                    <li>Log in to your License Spring dashboard</li>\n"
"                    <li>Create a new product</li>\n"
"                    <li>Get your Management API Key from: Account Settings → API Keys</li>\n"
"                    <li>Get your Shared Key from: Products → Your Product → SDK</li>\n"
"                    <li>Note your Product Code</li>\n"
"                </ol>\n"
"                <p>You'll need: <strong>Management API Key</strong>, <strong>Shared Key</strong>, and <strong>Product Code</strong></p>\n"
"            "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"                <h3>Pengaturan License Spring</h3> <ol> <li>Buat akun License Spring di <a href=\"https://licensespring.com\" target=\"_blank\">licensespring.com</a></li> <li>Masuk ke dashboard License Spring Anda</li> <li>Buat produk baru</li> <li>Dapatkan Management API Key Anda dari: Pengaturan Akun → API Keys</li> <li>Dapatkan Shared Key Anda dari: Produk → Produk Anda → SDK</li> <li>Catat kode produk Anda</li> </ol> <p>Anda memerlukan: <strong>Management API Key</strong>, <strong>Shared Key</strong>, dan <strong>Kode Produk</strong></p>\n"
"            "

msgid ""
"\n"
"                <h3>Cryptlex Setup</h3>\n"
"                <ol>\n"
"                    <li>Sign up for Cryptlex at <a href=\"https://cryptlex.com\" target=\"_blank\">cryptlex.com</a></li>\n"
"                    <li>Log in to your Cryptlex dashboard</li>\n"
"                    <li>Create a new product</li>\n"
"                    <li>Generate a Personal Access Token: Profile → Access Tokens → Create Token</li>\n"
"                    <li>Note your Account ID and Product ID</li>\n"
"                </ol>\n"
"                <p>You'll need: <strong>Access Token</strong>, <strong>Product ID</strong>, and <strong>Account ID</strong></p>\n"
"            "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"                <h3>Pengaturan Cryptlex</h3> <ol> <li>Buat akun Cryptlex di <a href=\"https://cryptlex.com\" target=\"_blank\">cryptlex.com</a></li> <li>Masuk ke dashboard Cryptlex Anda</li> <li>Buat produk baru</li> <li>Generasikan Token Akses Pribadi: Profil → Token Akses → Buat Token</li> <li>Catat ID Akun dan ID Produk Anda</li> </ol> <p>Anda memerlukan: <strong>Token Akses</strong>, <strong>ID Produk</strong>, dan <strong>ID Akun</strong></p>\n"
"            "

msgid ""
"\n"
"                <h3>Custom API Setup</h3>\n"
"                <p>This option allows you to integrate with your own license server.</p>\n"
"                <div class=\"alert alert-warning\">\n"
"                    <strong>Requirements:</strong> Your license server must implement the required REST API endpoints.\n"
"                    <a href=\"/docs/custom-license-api/\" target=\"_blank\">View API specification</a>\n"
"                </div>\n"
"                <ol>\n"
"                    <li>Ensure your license server is accessible via HTTPS</li>\n"
"                    <li>Prepare your API base URL (e.g., https://licenses.yoursite.com/api)</li>\n"
"                    <li>Prepare your authentication credentials</li>\n"
"                    <li>Map your API endpoints to Spwig operations</li>\n"
"                </ol>\n"
"                <p>You'll need: <strong>API Base URL</strong> and <strong>Authentication Credentials</strong></p>\n"
"            "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"                <h3>Pengaturan API Kustom</h3> <p>Opsi ini memungkinkan Anda mengintegrasikan dengan server lisensi Anda sendiri.</p> <div class=\"alert alert-warning\"> <strong>Kebutuhan:</strong> Server lisensi Anda harus menerapkan endpoint REST API yang diperlukan. <a href=\"/docs/custom-license-api/\" target=\"_blank\">Lihat spesifikasi API</a> </div> <ol> <li>Pastikan server lisensi Anda dapat diakses melalui HTTPS</li> <li>Siapkan URL dasar API Anda (misalnya, https://licenses.yoursite.com/api)</li> <li>Siapkan kredensial otentikasi Anda</li> <li>Petakan endpoint API Anda ke operasi Spwig</li> </ol> <p>Anda memerlukan: <strong>URL Dasar API</strong> dan <strong>Kredensial Otentikasi</strong></p>\n"
"            "

